      "message": "I don\u0027t say the fail-fast pattern is universally accepted practice (e.g. some functional languages tend to avoid early returns), but it\u0027s a recommended practice in Go.\nhttps://github.com/golang/go/wiki/CodeReviewComments#indent-error-flow",
