      "lineNbr": 133,
      "author": {
        "id": 1306673
      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-05-27T08:18:02Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think here we can also ignore such files and log some error message. It isn\u0027t common that someone will export errors as . or _. Nya, WDYT?",
      "parentUuid": "be9e42e5_5d547290",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 133,
        "startChar": 5,
        "endLine": 133,
        "endChar": 94
