      "writtenOn": "2021-06-08T19:10:40Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "IMO using alias for `errors` package is something we should not handle just because nobody using it.\nPlease check here:\nhttps://source.chromium.org/search?q\u003d%22chromiumos%2Ftast%2Ferrors%22\u0026start\u003d1\n\nSo we basically should always import `errors` without alias and if there is already alias for this package, report error.",
